    "final_verdict": "Otherly shows significant promise but requires substantial development before being viable for healthcare deployment. Key recommendations: 1) Develop comprehensive privacy and security protocols, 2) Conduct clinical validation studies, 3) Address regulatory compliance requirements, 4) Reduce third-party dependencies, 5) Create clear success metrics. The project scores above average overall (6.5/10) due to its strong potential impact and innovative approach, but needs refinement in implementation and presentation. The team should focus on addressing the identified gaps while maintaining their strong foundation in AI technology and user-centered design."
